story.title: Minnows Uruguay stun Fiji 30-27 at Rugby World Cup
story.summary: South American minnows Uruguay stunned Fiji 30-27 on Wednesday for their first Rugby World Cup win since 2003 and the first upset of the tournament in Japan.Uruguay scored three tries to turn 24-12 ahead against a second-string Fiji outfit and then clung on in the second half to record the biggest victory in their history.th/ric

xmlText.p: South American minnows Uruguay stunned Fiji 30-27 on Wednesday for their first Rugby World Cup win since 2003 and the first upset of the tournament in Japan.
Uruguay scored three tries to turn 24-12 ahead against a second-string Fiji outfit and then clung on in the second half to record the biggest victory in their history.
